{"article_id":"P3NOd6Oz2L0H9kcP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House has not yet decided how it will implement the president 's ban on transgender people","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"serving in the US military .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Mr Trump 's surprise Twitter announcement on Wednesday has been met with criticism from rights groups .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Spokeswoman Sarah Huckabee Sanders said","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"the administration would work alongside the Pentagon","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to decide how to proceed .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"It is not yet clear how the announcement will affect current transgender service personnel .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Transgender service members have expressed concern","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that they will be discharged , or unable to re-enlist .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"The timing also appears to have caught defence officials by surprise .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"`` The United States government will not accept or allow transgender individuals to serve in any capacity in the US military , ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Donald Trump tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"`` Our military must be focused on decisive and overwhelming victory","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and can not be burdened with the tremendous medical costs and disruption","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that transgender in the military would entail . ''","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"He added","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that the decision came `` after consultation with my Generals and military experts '' .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Some US media outlets have questioned the spending justification .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The Washington Post drew attention to an analysis","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that the US military spends almost $ 42m","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"( £32m )","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"a year on the erectile dysfunction medication Viagra","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"- several times the total estimated cost of transgender medical support .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Asked at a press briefing","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"if troops on battlefields would be immediately sent back ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Ms Huckabee Sanders said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"the policy had yet to be worked out .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"`` The decision is based on a military decision .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"It 's not meant to be anything more than that , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"On Wednesday , the defence department referred all queries to the White House .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Defence Secretary James Mattis was only told of the decision","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"after Mr Trump made his announcement .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"However , Ms Huckabee Sanders said :","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"`` This was something","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that was the product of consultation . ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"The timing of this transgender ban is almost as interesting as the move itself .","depth":3},{"id":37,"text":"Why now ?","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"With the Trump administration being buffeted by the Jeff Sessions political death watch , the ongoing multi-prong investigation into the Trump campaign , the healthcare drama in the Senate and the impending Russian sanctions bill ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"perhaps the administration decided","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"this was a good time","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"to change the subject","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and rally conservative forces to his side .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Republicans have long used cultural issues as a wedge","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to divide Democrats","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and energise evangelicals .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"While Mr Trump campaigned as sympathetic to LGBT rights ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"he needs the traditional religious conservatives to stay loyal to him now , more than ever .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"The independent Rand Corporation estimates","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that about 4,000 US active-duty and reserve service members are transgender ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"although some campaigners put the figure higher than 10,000 .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"The Obama administration announced last year","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that transgender people would be allowed to serve openly in the military .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Then-defence secretary Ash Carter also set a deadline of one year","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"for the various branches of the military to begin accepting transgender recruits .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"However in June , Mr Mattis agreed to a further six-month delay .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"The Obama-era policy had included a provision","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"for the military to provide medical help for service members","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"wanting to change gender .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Rand predicted","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that the inclusion of transgender people in the military would lead to a 0.13 % increase in healthcare spending","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"- approximately $ 8.4m .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Army reservist Rudy Akbarian told a news conference :","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"`` The discrimination","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"I 'm facing now","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"is from those outside the military","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"- not the people","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"who work with me . ''","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that `` not everyone responded well","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"after learning","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"I was transitioning .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"after spending time on missions","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"and realising","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"we all share the same love for the country ,","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"we worked together","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and got the job done . '' told a news conference :","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` The discrimination","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"I 'm facing now","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"is from those outside the military","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"- not the people","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"who work with me . ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"that `` not everyone responded well","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"after learning","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"I was transitioning .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"after spending time on missions","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"and realising","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"we all share the same love for the country ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"we worked together","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and got the job done . ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Meanwhile , Kristin Beck , a retired elite Navy SEAL , told Business Insider","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"that `` being transgender does n't affect anyone else ''","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"and that during her decorated military career , she had been `` defending individual liberty '' .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"`` If you ca n't defend that for everyone","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that 's an American citizen ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"that 's not right . ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Former Defence Secretary Ash Carter said :","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"`` To choose service members on other grounds than military qualifications is social policy","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"and has no place in our military . ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"said :","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"`` To choose service members on other grounds than military qualifications is social policy","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"and has no place in our military . ''","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Chairman of the Senate Armed Services Committee , Republican John McCain , said :","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"`` Any American","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"who meets current medical and readiness standards","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"should be allowed to continue serving . '' said :","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"`` Any American","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"who meets current medical and readiness standards","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"should be allowed to continue serving . ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Several British military generals condemned Mr Trump 's decision ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"including the commander of the UK Maritime Forces , Rear Admiral Alex Burton ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"who said :","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"`` We have a justifiably rigorous selection process","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"but it does n't include discrimination","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"and we 're a better fighting force for it '' .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"However , supporters said","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"the cost of transgender surgeries should not be funded by the military .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":239,"left":155,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":128,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":122,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":121,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":3,"right":123,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":126,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":135,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":9,"right":134,"relation":"organization","nuclea